TEXT 80 48 Left 2 ;V2L System — Vehicle-to-Load Power Electronics Simulation
TEXT 80 80 Left 2 ;Module A (left): 230V AC grid + diode bridge + 1000uF smoothing cap
TEXT 80 112 Left 2 ;Module B (centre-left): 400V EV traction battery with 0.5 ohm internal resistance
TEXT 80 144 Left 2 ;Module C (centre-right): H-bridge inverter + 10mH/4.7uF LC filter + 50-ohm load
TEXT 80 176 Left 2 ;Module D (bottom): 50Hz sine reference + 20kHz triangular carrier + gate comparators
TEXT 80 208 Left 2 ;OUTPUT: ~229 V RMS / 50 Hz  |  For 120V/60Hz: change Vref to SINE(0 0.524 60)
