TEXT 80 1552 Left 2 !.model D1N4007 D(Is=7.02767n Rs=0.0341512 N=1.80803 Cjo=2.6e-11 M=0.333 Vj=0.7 Bv=1000 Ibv=5e-08 Tt=1e-07)
